Food Truck Face Off - Season 1, Episode 10




Rivalries at the Roundhouse

In Toronto, Canada, host Jesse Palmer has two intense Sell Days in store for two lucky teams vying for the keys to their dream: their very own food truck for a year! Humiliation and maneuver missteps await the teams in an overwhelming first day. In the second day, they fight to successfully hustle customers alongside the big boys of established food trucks in downtown Toronto.




Original Air Date: 27-Nov-2014
